ARINC615OADLFData.LoadConditionText: Select RDCP, FRDC, or FUEL LRM to start the Loading process. Note - Program Enable discrete to ON, SAL label 114 available within 2 minutes from power on

InitiatedTestData.Name: Channel A Fuel Low Level Discrete Output Test
Channel A Refuel Solenoid Valve Command Test
Channel A Defuel Shutoff Valve Command Test

FailureData.Author: Parker FSD
FailureData.FailureName: Left Wing Tank Probe Return Signal Fault
FailureData.FailureMessage: Wiring Issue with the Left Wing Tank Probe Return signals to FRDC1
FailureData.MaintenanceText: Check Labels 351, and 352 for specific faults. Check the wiring from FRDC1 to the Tank unit.

FailureData.Author: Parker FSD
FailureData.FailureName: Left Wing Tank Probe Excitation Signal Fault
FailureData.FailureMessage: Wiring Issue with the Left Wing Tank Excitation Signals from FRDC1 to the Probes
FailureData.MaintenanceText: Check Labels 343, 344, 351, and 352 for faults. Test Wiring from FRDC1 to Tank Units, Replace FRDC1 if problem persists.

FailureData.Author: Parker FSD
FailureData.FailureName: Left Wing Tank Harness Shield Fault
FailureData.FailureMessage: Wiring Issue with Left Wing Tank Harness Shield to FRDC1
FailureData.MaintenanceText: Check Labels 343 and 344 for faults. Test wiring from FRDC1 to the Tank units. If wiring is good then replace FRDC1.

FailureData.Author: Parker FSD
FailureData.FailureName: Left Wing Tank Densitometer Fault
FailureData.FailureMessage: Left Wing Tank Densitometer has not been detected
FailureData.MaintenanceText: Check L340 for Specific Faults. 1-Test the Wiring from FRDC1 to the densitometer. 2-If wiring is not the issue replace the densitometer.

FailureData.Author: Parker FSD
FailureData.FailureName: Right Wing Tank Densitometer Fault
FailureData.FailureMessage: Right Wing Tank Densitometer has not been detected
FailureData.MaintenanceText: Check L340 for Specific Faults. 1-Test the Wiring from FRDC2 to the densitometer. 2-If wiring is not the issue replace the densitometer.

FailureData.Author: Parker FSD
FailureData.FailureName: FRDC1 - Center Tank Probe Return Signal Fault
FailureData.FailureMessage: Wiring issue between FRDC1 and Probe Return Signals in the Center Tank
FailureData.MaintenanceText: Check Label 355 specific faults. Check the wiring from FRDC1 to the Tank unit.

FailureData.Author: Parker FSD
FailureData.FailureName: FRDC2 - Center Tank Probe Return Signal Fault
FailureData.FailureMessage: Wiring issue between FRDC2 and Probe Return Signals in the Center Tank
FailureData.MaintenanceText: Check Label 355 specific faults. Check the wiring from FRDC2 to the Tank unit.

FailureData.Author: Parker FSD
FailureData.FailureName: FRDC1 - Center Tank Probe Excitation Signal Fault
FailureData.FailureMessage: Wiring Issue between the FRDC1 Excitation Signals and the Probes in the Center Tank
FailureData.MaintenanceText: Check Label 341, 351, and 352 specific faults. Check the wiring from FRDC1 to the Tank unit. Replace FRDC1 if problem persists.

FailureData.Author: Parker FSD
FailureData.FailureName: FRDC2 - Center Tank Probe Excitation Signal Fault
FailureData.FailureMessage: Wiring Issue between the FRDC2 Excitation Signals and the Probes in the Center Tank
FailureData.MaintenanceText: Check Label 342, 353, and 354 specific faults. Check the wiring from FRDC2 to the Tank unit. Replace FRDC2 if problem persists.

FailureData.Author: Parker FSD
FailureData.FailureName: FRDC1 - Center Tank Harness Shield Fault
FailureData.FailureMessage: Wiring Issue from the Center Tank Harness Shield to FRDC1
FailureData.MaintenanceText: Check Label 341 specific faults. Check the wiring from FRDC1 to the Tank unit. Replace FRDC1 if problem persists.

FailureData.Author: Parker FSD
FailureData.FailureName: FRDC2 - Center Tank Harness Shield Fault
FailureData.FailureMessage: Wiring Issue from the Center Tank Harness Shield to FRDC2
FailureData.MaintenanceText: Check Label 342 specific faults. Check the wiring from FRDC2 to the Tank unit. Replace FRDC2 if problem persists.

FailureData.Author: Parker FSD
FailureData.FailureName: Right Wing Tank Probe Return Signal Fault
FailureData.FailureMessage: Wiring Issue with the Right Wing Tank Probe Return signals to FRDC2
FailureData.MaintenanceText: Check Labels 353, and 354 for specific faults. Check the wiring from FRDC2 to the Tank unit.

FailureData.Author: Parker FSD
FailureData.FailureName: Right Wing Tank Probe Excitation Signal Fault
FailureData.FailureMessage: Wiring Issue with the Right Wing Tank Excitation Signals from FRDC2 to the Probes
FailureData.MaintenanceText: Check Labels 345, 346, 353, and 354 for faults. Test Wiring from FRDC2 to Tank Units, Replace FRDC2 if problem persists.

FailureData.Author: Parker FSD
FailureData.FailureName: Right Wing Tank Harness Shield Fault
FailureData.FailureMessage: Wiring Issue with Right Wing Tank Harness Shield to FRDC2
FailureData.MaintenanceText: Check Labels 345 and 346 for faults. Test wiring from FRDC2 to the Tank units. If wiring is good then replace FRDC2.

FailureData.Author: Parker FSD
FailureData.FailureName: Fuel LRM - A/C Configuration Fault
FailureData.FailureMessage: Fuel LRM is reporting an Aircraft Configuration Strapping Fault. Harness may not be connected properly or possible recessed pins.
FailureData.MaintenanceText: Check L347 for FLRM CHA and CHB Strapping Faults. Check the Parity and LBS/KGS setting. Check the connection of the wire harness to the Fuel LRM.

FailureData.Author: Parker FSD
FailureData.FailureName: Fuel LRM Fault
FailureData.FailureMessage: Fuel LRM Hardware Fault
FailureData.MaintenanceText: Check the power input to the Fuel LRM. Replace the Fuel LRM

FailureData.Author: Parker FSD
FailureData.FailureName: Fuel LRM - A429 Communication Fault
FailureData.FailureMessage: Fuel LRM reporting a communication issue with RDIU 7 and RDIU 9
FailureData.MaintenanceText: Check wiring from RDIU 7 and RDIU 9 to the Fuel LRM

FailureData.Author: Parker FSD
FailureData.FailureName: FRDC Fault
FailureData.FailureMessage: Fuel LRM is reporting a FRDC Software Configuration Mismatch
FailureData.MaintenanceText: Update the Software on both FRDCs to the latest version

FailureData.Author: Parker FSD
FailureData.FailureName: L Temperature Sensor LCC_RTD_01 Fault
FailureData.FailureMessage: Left Wing Tank Temperature Sensor wiring issue
FailureData.MaintenanceText: Check the wiring from FRDC1 to the Temperature Sensor. Replace Temperature Sensor.

FailureData.Author: Parker FSD
FailureData.FailureName: R Temperature Sensor RCC_RTD_01 Fault
FailureData.FailureMessage: Right Wing Tank Temperature Sensor wiring issue
FailureData.MaintenanceText: Check the wiring from FRDC2 to the Temperature Sensor. Replace Temperature Sensor.

FailureData.Author: Parker FSD
FailureData.FailureName: RDCP Fault
FailureData.FailureMessage: Fuel LRM reporting an issue with the RDCP; possible communication issue, or RDCP internal fault
FailureData.MaintenanceText: Check the wiring to the Refuel Panel. Replace the Refuel Defuel Control Panel.

FailureData.Author: Parker FSD
FailureData.FailureName: FRDC Communication Fault
FailureData.FailureMessage: Fuel LRM reporting an issue communicating to the FRDC over CAN BUS
FailureData.MaintenanceText: Check the wiring between the FRDC and the Fuel LRM. If wiring good, then problem is either the FRDC or Fuel LRM.

FailureData.Author: Parker FSD
FailureData.FailureName: C1 PUMP INHIBIT FAULT
FailureData.FailureMessage: C1 Pump is supposed to be inhibited, but not responding to command.
FailureData.MaintenanceText: Test wiring from the Fuel LRM to L CTR AC PUMP CONTROL RELAY 1, MODE SEL PBA to the L CTR AC PUMP CONTROL RELAY 1

FailureData.Author: Parker FSD
FailureData.FailureName: C2 PUMP INHIBIT FAULT
FailureData.FailureMessage: C2 Pump is supposed to be inhibited, but not responding to command.
FailureData.MaintenanceText: Test wiring from the Fuel LRM to R CTR AC PUMP CONTROL RELAY 1, MODE SEL PBA to the R CTR AC PUMP CONTROL RELAY 1
